th it \u2014 my daughter hasn''t taken hers off. If you''ve been on the fence, this is your sign to just go look.", "description": "Mom-approved spring picks. You''re gonna want to see this collection. \ud83c\udf37", "call_to_action": "SHOP_NOW", "utm_content": "ad_l2_story_static_collection", "image_url": "https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/I/61BC8vDhz5L.jpg"}]}, "utm_auto": true}', '{}', 1, 'exported', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-29 11:44:23', '2026-04-29 11:44:31', '2026-04-29 11:44:31', NULL);
INSERT INTO public.campaigns_v3 (id, creator_id, package_type, target_type, target_value, brand_slug, product_slug, product_name, destination_url, layers_json, asset_url, asset_type, package_json, defaults_overrides_json, utm_auto, status, meta_campaign_ids_json, meta_post_id, notes, created_at, updated_at, exported_at, built_at) VALUES (2, 'everydaywithsteph', 'new_campaign', 'asin', 'B08C3LF6FK', 'nostalgia', 'nostalgia-vintage-hard-and-sug', 'Nostalgia Vintage Hard and Sugar Free Candy Countertop Cotton Candy Maker Includes 2 Reusable Cones And Sugar Scoop – Pink', 'https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08C3LF6FK?tag=mommymedeals-20', '["L1", "L2", "L3"]', 'https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71gvwKoU+QL._AC_SY300_SX300_.jpg', 'static_image', '{"package_type": "new_campaign", "ad_account_id": "act_573934886369270", "page_id": "100065251532225", "brand": "nostalgia", "product": "Nostalgia Vintage Hard and Sugar Free Candy Countertop Cotton Candy Maker Includes 2 Reusable Cones And Sugar Scoop \u2013 Pink", "product_slug": "nostalgia-vintage-hard-and-sug", "destination_url": "https://www.amazon.com/dp/B08C3LF6FK?tag=mommymedeals-20", "layers": [{"layer_id": "L1", "name": "Evergreen", "daily_budget": 2500, "audience_type": "advantage_plus", "creative_ref": "AD_L1"}, {"layer_id": "L2", "name": "Story / Parent Voice", "daily_budget": 2500, "audience_type": "advantage_plus", "creative_ref": "AD_L2"}, {"layer_id": "L3", "name": "Retargeting", "daily_budget": 2500, "audience_type": "retargeting", "creative_ref": "AD_L3", "budget_type": "ABO", "retargeting_source": "page_engagers_14d"}], "creative": {"type": "static_image", "assets": [{"creative_ref": "AD_L1", "headline": "Cotton Candy at Home for $39.99", "body": "This pink cotton candy maker from Nostalgia is the real deal \ud83c\udfa1 Works with regular sugar OR sugar-free \u2014 comes with 2 reusable cones and a scoop, everything you need right out of the box. Under $40 for carnival magic in your kitchen? Yes please.", "description": "Nostalgia Cotton Candy Maker \u2013 pink, $39.99. Sugar & sugar-free compatible. 2 cones included.", "call_to_action": "SHOP_NOW", "utm_content": "ad_l1_evergreen_static", "image_url": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71gvwKoU+QL._AC_SY300_SX300_.jpg"}, {"creative_ref": "AD_L2", "headline": "My Kids Lost Their Minds \ud83d\ude02", "body": "Okay I was NOT prepared for how obsessed my kids would be with this thing \ud83e\ude77 We pulled it out on a random Tuesday and suddenly I''m the coolest mom on the block \u2014 homemade cotton candy in like 5 minutes. It''s $39.99 and honestly one of the best impulse buys I''ve made all year.", "description": "The cotton candy maker my kids are OBSESSED with \u2014 and it''s only $39.99. \ud83c\udf80", "call_to_action": "SHOP_NOW", "utm_content": "ad_l2_story_static", "image_url": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71gvwKoU+QL._AC_SY300_SX300_.jpg"}, {"creative_ref": "AD_L3", "headline": "Still Thinking About It? \ud83d\udc40", "body": "Hey, you looked at this cotton candy maker for a reason \ud83d\ude04 It''s still $39.99, still pink and adorable, and still making kids (and moms!) very very happy. Don''t let it sell out before you grab one \u2014 just saying \ud83c\udfa1", "description": "You saw it, you loved it \u2014 the $39.99 cotton candy maker is still waiting for you. \ud83e\ude77", "call_to_action": "GET_OFFER", "utm_content": "ad_l3_retargeting_static", "image_url": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71gvwKoU+QL._AC_SY300_SX300_.jpg"}]}, "utm_auto": true}', '{}', 1, 'draft', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-04-29 11:52:08', '2026-04-29 11:52:08', NULL, NULL);
