/m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71VbPmMdRBL._AC_SL1500_.jpg"}, {"creative_ref": "AD_L2", "headline": "I Hid This Chair From My Kids \ud83d\ude02", "body": "Okay not really \u2014 but the second I set up my Wise Owl hammock chair in the backyard, everyone wanted a turn. It rocks like a dream, packs up in seconds, and honestly? $94.99 was SO worth it. \ud83e\udde1", "description": "The chair that started a whole family argument \u2014 in the best way. Foldable, rockable, packable.", "call_to_action": "SHOP_NOW", "utm_content": "ad_l2_story_static", "image_url": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/71VbPmMdRBL._AC_SL1500_.jpg"}]}, "utm_auto": true}', '{}', 1, 'draft', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-05-06 11:43:48', '2026-05-06 11:43:48', NULL, NULL);
