jpg"}, {"creative_ref": "AD_L2", "headline": "My Kid Asks for This at Nap Time \ud83e\udd79", "body": "Honestly I was NOT prepared for how much my little one would love this mat \u2014 she drags it out even on weekends now \ud83d\ude02 The pillow and blanket are already attached so there''s nothing extra to pack, and at $32.98 I didn''t have to think twice. It''s one of those buys you wonder how you did preschool without.", "description": "Built-in pillow & blanket, cute name tag, easy carry handle. A nap mat she''ll actually love.", "call_to_action": "SHOP_NOW", "utm_content": "ad_l2_story_static", "image_url": "https://m.media-amazon.com/images/I/81bGSjV9KkL._AC_SL1500_.jpg"}]}, "utm_auto": true}', '{}', 1, 'draft', NULL, NULL, NULL, '2026-05-06 11:43:56', '2026-05-06 11:43:56', NULL, NULL);
